Drop WhatsApp chat exports here before running:
  python scripts/import_chat_exports.py

Filename convention (required — phone cannot be recovered from the
export body):

  {phone_digits}_{DisplayName}.txt

Examples:
  972544848291_Noam.txt
  972523955056_Daniel.txt

Dashes in {DisplayName} are rendered as spaces in the imported
household + member record.
